subject: Golf
United States Women's Open (Golf)
lead_paragraph: Stacy Lewis had a one-over-par 73 for a one-stroke lead over Amy Yang after the third round of the Honda L.P.G.A. Thailand in Chonburi. Yang birdied the final two holes for a 71.
